name: Scandinavian Airlines A350 Inaugural First Flight
description:
Scandinavian Airlines recently launched a brand new airplane. The Scandinavian Airlines A350 represents some of the best the company has to offer. In this video, we'll explore the Copenhagen Airport, the Scandinavian Airlines A350 in Business Class and Economy, as well as all of the celebrations that accompanied the excitement surrounding the first day the Scandinavian Airlines A350 took to the skies. 

As an aviation enthusiast, I'm not sure I enjoy anything quite as much as an inaugural flight and to have the chance to be one of the first to fly on Scandinavian Airlines' A350 was even more special since I had almost no experience with Scandinavian Airlines before this.
